{
  "stem": "1799.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 533.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The war broke out in 1939, and I think France fell in May of 1940.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So this was, again, springtime.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was the end of our home, and it was the end of a peaceful time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Germans were in command.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What happened then?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The children were taken, some to various homes in Paris, homes that were controlled by the O.S.E.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I went to a private school, along with three other of the students in Paris, to a school in the community of Clamart-- C-L-A-M-A-R-T-- very strict school.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And by the summer-- when was it by the fall of 1940-- a organization had helped the O.S.E. and our group to bring us together into a home south of the demarcation line of France, which by then had been established by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "France was divvied up-- the northern part, occupied France, and the southern part, which they called Free France, which was run by Vichy, which was run by Laval.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But since this was so early in the game in 1940, no one knew that there was going to be a concerted effort to not allow Jews to stay.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was to come.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we then went to this home in Chabannes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I left the private school I had been in about five months.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the group, plus other children that came from other parts of France, and even Europe, got together in this home called Chabannes, a community near Limoges in the Department of Creuse.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Chabannes was a village.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It had a private-- it had a small public school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was a home that housed-- it was a coed home-- I would say about 180 children.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And about a third of them were girls.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
